<h3>Starting Your Vegan Baking Journey</h3>
<p>Begin by selecting simple recipes that highlight these ingredients and methods. Focus on baked goods like muffins, cookies, pancakes, and quick breads to build confidence. As you grow comfortable, venture into more complex recipes like layer cakes or pastries.</p>
